": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031413_535452635889052_1371977149700678380_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=A7-DZkaF2AUQ7kNvgEt41QI&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCvMl4h5aCjQCyuQEpa_179jFxc885hxamz0kL0QlVGUw&oe=674874D2"}, "display_name": "Track Craft", "keywords": ["track", "craft", "racing", "car", "mixed"], "long_description": "**Track Craft is a VR racing game where you drive tiny cars, craft gravity-defying tracks, and race other players daily on new circuits. \n\nCraft, Share, Race, Repeat.**\n\n\n# GET BEHIND THE WHEEL\n\nExperience the 104 pre-built tracks spread across 5 different worlds. Each bringing new mechanics, challenges, cars, and skins to unlock.\n\n{2499265100265459}\n\n\n# CRAFT YOUR OWN TRACKS\n\nCreate tracks intuitively thanks to full hand tracking and share them online. Or just race on new tracks created by the community every day.\n\n{1695057567991201}\n\n\n# BUILD UP YOUR COLLECTION\n\nUnlock new exciting cars by collecting stars.\n\n{850050203892697}\n\n\n# ONLINE MULTIPLAYER\n\nPlay and Craft with your friends at home or online with players across the globe.\n\n{1046525373656002}\n\n\n# ULTIMATE MR PLAYGROUND \n\nUse your surroundings and turn them into a mixed-reality race track.\n\n{1272215014134973}\n\n\n\n\n\n\n# THE FUN NEVER ENDS\n\n\n\nAvailable on Quest 3, Quest Pro, and Quest 2.", "short_description": "Track Craft is a VR racing game where you drive tiny cars, craft gravity-defying tracks, and race other players daily on new circuits. \n\nCraft, Share, Race, Repeat."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.gamify.cz/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.gamify.cz/terms-of-service", "publisher_name": "Brainz Gamify s.r.o.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.trackcraft.cz/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534"